# AcademiCLI

A CLI tool to fetch Google Scholar metrics for researchers.

## Installation
```bash
pip install academiCLI
```

## Usage
```bash
academiCLI --name "Albert Einstein"
```

## Features
- Get h-index and citation counts
- Interactive author selection
- Multiple results handling
